OL,4,CKohli's teenage killer to be heard
OL,5,Cnext week
OL,7,FA bid to have the sentence of a
OL,8,Fteenage boy who killed elderly dog
OL,9,Fwalker Bhim Kohli increased is due to
OL,10,Fbe heard at the Court of Appeal on
OL,11,FWednesday.
OL,13,FMr Kohli, 80, was punched and kicked,
OL,14,Fslapped in the face with a shoe and
OL,15,Fracially abused in an attack in
OL,16,FFranklin Park, Braunstone Town, near
OL,17,FLeicester, on September 1 last year,
OL,18,Fand died the next day.
