OL,4,CKohli's teenage killer to be heard
OL,5,Cnext week
OL,7,FThe teenager, who cannot be named for
OL,8,Flegal reasons, was convicted of
OL,9,Fmanslaughter and sentenced to seven
OL,10,Fyears' custody in June, when he was
OL,11,Faged 15.
OL,13,FThe Attorney General's Office (AGO)
OL,14,Fannounced in July that the Solicitor
OL,15,FGeneral, Lucy Rigby, had referred the
OL,16,Fsentence to the Court of Appeal under
OL,17,Fthe unduly lenient sentence scheme.
