OL,3,CBid to increase sentence of Bhim
OL,4,CKohli's teenage killer to be heard
OL,5,Cnext week
OL,7,FCourt listings show that the bid to
OL,8,Fincrease the sentence is due to be
OL,9,Fheard at the Court of Appeal in London
OL,10,Fon Wednesday, with the boy also
OL,11,Fseeking to appeal against his sentence
OL,12,Fat the same hearing.
OL,14,FThe boy was convicted of manslaughter,
OL,15,Fbut cleared of murder, following a
OL,16,Ftrial at Leicester Crown Court.
OL,18,FHe was convicted alongside a 13-year-
OL,19,Fold girl, who encouraged the attack by
OL,20,Ffilming parts of it while laughing.
