OL,4,CKohli's teenage killer to be heard
OL,5,Cnext week
OL,7,FThe girl had filmed a series of video
OL,8,Fclips in which Mr Kohli was hit with
OL,9,Fthe shoe by the balaclava-clad boy and
OL,10,Fanother where the elderly man lay
OL,11,Fmotionless on the ground.
OL,13,FMr Kohli's children found him lying on
OL,14,Fthe ground in agony when he told his
OL,15,Fdaughter that he had been called a
OL,16,F"P***" during the attack.
