OL,7,FThe girl, who also cannot be named,
OL,8,Fwas sentenced to a three-year youth
OL,9,Frehabilitation order by Mr Justice
OL,10,FTurner, but her sentence has not been
OL,11,Freferred to the Court of Appeal.
OL,13,FAfter the sentencing, Mr Kohli's
OL,14,Fdaughter, Susan Kohli, said she was
OL,15,F"angry and disappointed" at the
OL,16,Fsentences, stating that she believed
OL,17,Fthey did not "reflect the severity of
OL,18,Fthe crime they committed".
