OL,7,FMid Leicestershire MP Peter Bedford
OL,8,Fand the MP for South Leicestershire,
OL,9,FAlberto Costa, also wrote to the AGO
OL,10,Fasking for the sentences to be
OL,11,Freviewed.
OL,13,FA spokesperson for the AGO said last
OL,14,Fmonth that Ms Rigby was "appalled by
OL,15,Fthis violent, cowardly attack on an
OL,16,Finnocent man".
